AIM:
To develop a simple Student Record System using Spring Data JPA that performs storing, retrieving, filtering, sorting, and paginating student records using JpaRepository.

PROCEDURE:
Create a Spring Boot project with dependencies: Spring Web, Spring Data JPA, H2 Database.
Create the Student entity using annotations like @Entity, @Id, @Column.
Create StudentRepository extending JpaRepository to perform database operations.
Write custom query methods (findByDepartment, findByAgeGreaterThan, sorting and pagination).
Create StudentService & StudentController to handle business logic and REST endpoints.
Run the application and test all operations using browser/Postman.

